casebody.data:
Donald J. TRUMP, President of the United States, et al., Petitioners,
v.
PENNSYLVANIA, et al. No. 19-454. Supreme Court of the United States. Jan. 17, 2020.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the *919Third Circuit granted. The cases is consolidated, and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
